name: Hamunaptra Style
description:
This is a Style embedding which turns everything in your image towards an Ancient Egyptian style! Think Pyramids, the river Nile, and Pharaohs! Simply throw Style-Hamunaptra on to the end of your prompt (or the start, if the effect doesn't come through strong enough), and bam! - your picture is now Egypt-ified - it's as easy as that.

+10 internet points for getting the name reference.

You can combine this embedding with other embeddings!

Please consider joining my Patreon! Advanced SD tutorials, settings explanations, adult-art, from a female content creator (me!) patreon.com/theally
